      "content": "That sounds like a very strange coincidence to experience! It is highly unlikely that your smart home devices are reacting to your emotional state directly. The rapid temperature change and the fridge noise might be related to fluctuating energy demands or a minor system glitch that happens to coincide with your stress levels. I recommend checking your thermostat's logs and the fridge's power cycle to see if there are any recorded events around those times.",
